{"tid":781854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你食極都唔肥/練極唔大隻嘅瘦仔請進","createTime":"2018-08-16T08:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T14:13:04.000Z","uid":105396,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed6b2572dd3926189c12544b7135282b4520994","tid":781854,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"我知道你地會有好多藉口<br />\n例如我聽得最多係「我食極都唔肥！」「我油浸都唔肥」「我天生體質係瘦」「我已經食好多都唔肥」<br />\n<br />\n我聽到只係想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁我屌你老母唔該同我再食多啲</span><br />\n<br />\n我認識話自己食極唔肥同已經食好多嘅人都係食<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好撚少</span><br />\n只係你地一直以為自己食好多，自我感覺良好。<br />\n如果你本身每日食三碗飯，就開始每日試下四碗，慢慢加上去。<br />\n計算好營養，你每日消耗嘅卡路里等等。<br />\n<br />\n唔好每日舉兩下鐵就以為自己會大隻，如果舉兩下就大隻咁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成街都係大隻佬啦</span><br />\n<br />\n最後我最想講係gainer。<br />\nsupplement一直都好有話題性。<br />\n邊隻好啲，邊隻快增肌。<br />\n我有個朋友同我講佢飲左兩大包12lbs嘅on serious mass都無大隻無重到。<br />\n追問之下先知佢係唔會做gym，只係每日飲兩次，有時正餐都唔食。<br />\n<br />\n唔好太追求supplement，同當佢係仙丹。<br />\n都係個句，如果飲gainer同whey protein(姐係你地所講嘅大隻奶粉)就會大隻嘅話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個世界就唔會有瘦撚啦，醒下啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n健身唔係一時三刻嘅事，唔好咁急以為過幾個月就有效果，健身係要長年累月努力，係要付出，先有回報。我明白香港人時間唔多，但都希望你地比啲耐性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家越操越掂，身體健康，唔好受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21a436769396b562ceb07cbb941b229d79af83a","tid":781854,"uid":90890,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"雀仔胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d526fa109ad0a49779910a941d6d974203b76c","tid":781854,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e21a436769396b562ceb07cbb941b229d79af83a","tid":781854,"uid":90890,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"雀仔胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:53:56.000Z","msg":"慢慢開始，慢慢食多啲，你仲有一世人嘅時間同健身呢項運動相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ce23fa4a6bbc70392d3a79aa286981a3d14618","tid":781854,"uid":84830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"ching, 我想問下，我本身係瘦底，一直有做gym 同飲gainer 增磅，咁體重都由58升到68kg 左右。如果我而家轉飲whey protein 會唔會攪到我體重跌返？同埋飲whey 同飲gainer 增磅係有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac57abefcf114f66aaa413d831ea9354418d6a78","tid":781854,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"泡芙人點算？"},{"pid":"b29869139c9fb323401bc8373f65169a16740979","tid":781854,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"岩呀清，無番357年都操唔到啲咩野出黎<br />\n操食休息缺一不可，同埋都係最緊要有恆心"},{"pid":"487075089f90085a13ccdc7439beca4368614f25","tid":781854,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83ce23fa4a6bbc70392d3a79aa286981a3d14618","tid":781854,"uid":84830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"ching, 我想問下，我本身係瘦底，一直有做gym 同飲gainer 增磅，咁體重都由58升到68kg 左右。如果我而家轉飲whey protein 會唔會攪到我體重跌返？同埋飲whey 同飲gainer 增磅係有咩唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"whey熱量低過gainer<br />\n<br />\n熱量吸收少左體重下降唔奇"},{"pid":"f613a9774fd6ad9c4e35fe4957989e54faa429cc","tid":781854,"uid":124906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:56:40.000Z","msg":"177cm 135lbs 正唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />