.000Z","msg":"其實無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前應該係太依賴粉，都係要靠自己食多啲先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789893502e37b1207f7bea6d8e5ec00972113c54","tid":781854,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:06:19.000Z","msg":"增重就我以言其實gainer真係唔算太必要<br />\n我以前增重一開始都飲gainer，之後都剩係飲whey，再加大份量嘅正餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你忙到無時間食正餐啦或者胃口細到好難食到足夠熱量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係gainer真係無咩必要"},{"pid":"456bae247756de0616a55c77a36ab5b7546fce56","tid":781854,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0da77cabdb183ea99de827dc837c48de1d4ec440","tid":781854,"uid":84830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1889549bef00c9d71d86fe99a7682db1c9278816","tid":781854,"uid":105396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9260d9bdf33e4c8bbe6ab886a3cb470ea20c565e","tid":781854,"uid":84830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"我有排飲過啲蛋白質量多啲、少啲carb 既粉，體重跌得好明顯，嚇到飲完之後即刻轉返gainer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:02:41.000Z","msg":"唔好太依靠粉阿！你仲有其他方法得到熱量"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"其實無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前應該係太依賴粉，都係要靠自己食多啲先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"係，始終supplement個作用都係本身食唔夠補返營養"},{"pid":"4ca519a4dbc77c721dcd08c1b5caff8db73c69a1","tid":781854,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"42a526b8a141305e608148620cedeb024df620bf","tid":781854,"uid":136881,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy"